verbose_text: Gregory et al reported that miR-200 and miR-205 could inhibit the zinc finger E-box-binding homeobox 1 (ZEB1) and ZEB2, ZEB1 (TCF8 / EF1) and ZEB2 [SMAD interacting protein 1 (SIP1)/ZFXH1B] and thus maintain the epithelial cell phenotype.
evidence: miR-200 and miR-205 could inhibit the zinc finger E-box-binding homeobox 1
